The paper discusses the use of quadrotors for infrastructure inspection and search-and-rescue, which are typical applications of robotics (cs.RO). The paper also discusses the use of receding-horizon planning and trajectory design, which are topics related to control systems (cs.SY). The use of zonotopes for online planning is a novel approach that can be considered as a machine learning technique (cs.LG). The paper also mentions the use of sensors and uncertainty, which are topics related to computer vision (cs.CV) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
